      <li><ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-300 my-2 ml-4">
      <li>How do Pantry and BCTV compare on (a) straight line computations and (b) random memory access?</li>
    </ol></li>
      <li><ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-300 my-2 ml-4">
      <li>What is the gain of Buffet's RAM abstraction (<a href="#page-8-0">&sect;3)</a>?</li>
    </ol></li>
      <li><ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-300 my-2 ml-4">
      <li>What is the gain of Buffet's flattening transformation (<a href="#page-12-0">&sect;4)</a>?</li>
    </ol></li>
